cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and natural language processing using deep learning models.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on phoneme recognition using speech signals.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of Word2vec and attention-based end-to-end models for improving the performance of the phoneme recognition system.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with the application of deep learning models for speech recognition.
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is also a possible category as the paper involves processing of speech signals for phoneme recognition.
